{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1976,"month":10,"day":21}],"page_start":3,"page_end":3,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"毛主席的教导刻心里","authors":["高玉宝"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"八亿神州齐哀悼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哀乐声声把心绞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泪水飞似倾盆雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往事桩桩心头绕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那万恶的旧社会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四海没有我的家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃糠咽菜披麻袋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给地主老财当牛马。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春雷一声震天响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东方升起红太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来了救星毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命人民有方向。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是您领我们扛起枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是您率我们打美蒋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三座大山全推倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国人民得解放！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是您教我学文化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是您教我写文章，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是您送我上大学，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的恩情永不忘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不忘一九五二年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢度国庆前一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然收到您的请帖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国徽耀眼镶金边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手捧请帖心潮翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热泪盈睡如清泉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧社会的放牛娃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新社会里赴国宴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热血沸腾情满腔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兴奋地走进怀仁堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望敬爱的毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红心向着红太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见到领袖热泪流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万岁万岁飞出口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手捧杯举过头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到您面前去敬酒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您叫我多到实践中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您叫我多写工农兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您叫我刻苦学马列，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您叫我终生为人民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的领袖毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我曾多次见到您，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每次见您力无穷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您的教导刻心里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远继承您遗志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远握紧枪和笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远歌颂工农兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继续革命志不移！"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}